<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<FrameLayout
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="#F1F6F9"
    tools:context=".fragments.lesson7.OverviewFragment">

    <androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView
        android:overScrollMode="never"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">
        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent"
                android:orientation="vertical">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="vertical">
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                        android:gravity="center_vertical"
                        android:text="Dividing Simple Fractions and Mixed Fractions"
                        android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Large"
                        android:textColor="@color/black" />
                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/btn_tts"
                        android:text="Read Aloud"
                        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                        android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                        android:drawableStart="@drawable/ic_text_to_speech"
                        android:textAllCaps="false"
                        android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                        android:paddingStart="10dp"
                        android:paddingEnd="20dp"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="48dp" />
                </LinearLayout>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_1"
                    android:text="Knowing about something is really important. Although it takes a lot of patience in applying some ways and means to find it but seeing the result is amazing. In dividing simple fractions and mixed fractions you will discover that even a little portion of an object can be measured and has value. The processes involve in solving the problems related to it will be discussed to you later. Further, the application of what you have learned is expected to be mastered in order to move on to the next level of learning."
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_2"
                    android:text="Understanding concepts in mathematics is indeed crucial, and it often requires patience and various problem-solving strategies to find solutions. Let's delve into the concepts of dividing simple fractions and mixed fractions, exploring the processes involved in solving problems related to them.\n\nDividing Simple Fractions:\nWhen dividing simple fractions, such as 3/4 ÷ 2/5, we follow a specific process:\n\nStep 1: Convert the division to multiplication.\nTo divide fractions, we can convert the division sign (÷) to a multiplication sign (×) and take the reciprocal of the divisor. In our example, 3/4 ÷ 2/5 becomes 3/4 × 5/2.\n\nStep 2: Multiply the numerators.\nMultiply the numerators (the numbers on top) together: 3 × 5 = 15.\nStep 3:\nMultiply the denominators.\nMultiply the denominators (the numbers on the bottom) together: 4 × 2 = 8.\n\nStep 4: Simplify, if necessary.\nIf possible, simplify the resulting fraction. In this case, 15/8 cannot be simplified further.\n\nThus, 3/4 ÷ 2/5 = 15/8.\n\nDividing Mixed Fractions:\nWhen dividing mixed fractions, such as 2 1/2 ÷ 1 3/4, we use a similar process:\n\nStep 1: Convert the mixed fractions to improper fractions.\nConvert both mixed fractions to improper fractions. In our example, 2 1/2 becomes 5/2, and 1 3/4 becomes 7/4.\n\nStep 2: Apply the same steps as dividing simple fractions.\nFollow the same steps as dividing simple fractions, i.e., convert the division to multiplication, take the reciprocal of the divisor, multiply the numerators, multiply the denominators, and simplify if necessary.\n\nIn our example, 2 1/2 ÷ 1 3/4 becomes 5/2 ÷ 7/4.\n\nStep 3: Multiply the numerators.\nMultiply the numerators together: 5 × 4 = 20.\n\nStep 4: Multiply the denominators.\nMultiply the denominators together: 2 × 7 = 14.\n\nStep 5: Simplify, if necessary.\nSimplify the resulting fraction. In this case, 20/14 can be simplified to 10/7.\n\nThus, 2 1/2 ÷ 1 3/4 = 10/7.\n\nApplying Learned Concepts:\nTo master mathematics, it is essential to apply what you have learned in order to advance to the next level of learning. Practice various problems and explore different scenarios to strengthen your understanding of dividing fractions.\n\nBy practicing and applying the concepts, you will become more proficient in solving problems involving fractions. As you progress, you will develop problem-solving skills and gain a deeper understanding of the value and measurement of even the smallest portions of objects.\n\nRemember, patience, practice, and perseverance are key when it comes to learning and excelling in mathematics."
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
            </LinearLayout>

                <LinearLayout
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="16dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                        app:cardElevation="0dp"
                        app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent">
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="vertical"
                            android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_tutorial"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="match_parent">
                            <TextView
                                android:text="Tutorial"
                                android:textSize="18sp"
                                android:paddingTop="10dp"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:textColor="@color/black"
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <TextView
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:textColor="@color/black"
                                android:text="Are you struggling with the numbers mixing in your head? In this tutorial, we will guide you through the step-by-step process of this lesson!"
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <Button
                                android:id="@+id/btn_tutorial"
                                android:text="Watch Tutorial"
                                android:textAllCaps="false"
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                android:textColor="@color/black"
                                android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                                android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="150dp"
                                android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                        </LinearLayout>
                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                    <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                        app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                        app:cardElevation="0dp"
                        app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                        android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="vertical"
                            android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_quiz"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="match_parent">
                            <TextView
                                android:text="Quiz"
                                android:textSize="18sp"
                                android:paddingTop="10dp"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:textColor="@color/white"
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="horizontal"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <ImageView
                                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                                    android:background="@drawable/bg_list"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <LinearLayout
                                    android:orientation="vertical"
                                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="10"
                                        android:textSize="18sp"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="True or False Questions"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                </LinearLayout>
                            </LinearLayout>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="horizontal"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <ImageView
                                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                                    android:background="@drawable/bg_clock"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <LinearLayout
                                    android:orientation="vertical"
                                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="1 min"
                                        android:textSize="18sp"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="Per Questions"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                </LinearLayout>
                            </LinearLayout>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="horizontal"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <ImageView
                                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                                    android:background="@drawable/bg_trophy"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <LinearLayout
                                    android:orientation="vertical"
                                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="50%"
                                        android:textSize="18sp"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                    <TextView
                                        android:text="To Passed the Quiz"
                                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                        android:textColor="@color/white"
                                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                </LinearLayout>
                            </LinearLayout>
                            <TextView
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:text="Let's measure your problem-solving skills to assess your level of understanding."
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                android:textColor="@color/white"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <Button
                                android:id="@+id/btn_start_quiz"
                                android:text="Start Quiz!"
                                android:textAllCaps="false"
                                android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                android:textColor="@color/white"
                                android:background="@drawable/btn_primary_button"
                                android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                                android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                                android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="150dp"
                                android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                        </LinearLayout>
                    </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                </LinearLayout>

        </LinearLayout>
    </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>
</FrameLayout>